text: Rolf Streuli (born 13 July 1931) is a Swiss rower. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics in Rome with the men's coxless four where they came sixth. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Switzerland Category:Rowers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Zürich Category:European Rowing Championships medalists
